'''Kuwait''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in December 2019. Its default cities are the capital, Kuwait City, along with Al Ahmadi.

In December 2019 on iOS; new countries were added. Along with Kuwait; there was also Austria, Bahamas, Costa Rica, DR Congo, Kazakhstan, Kenya, Lebanon, Mongolia, Nepal, Ukraine, and Vietnam. This was added in the ''Friends'' Update.

